    <h1>
      Selecting and moving Units
    </h1>
        <h4>Selecting one unit</h4>
        <p>
        There are no special select features yet. Just click on the unit.<br><br>
        </p>
        <h4>Selecting more units</h4>
        <p>
        Hold down the left mouse button and encircle the units you like to select.<br><br>
        </p>
        <h4>Moving a unit:</h4>
        <p>
        Select a unit or a group and click with the right mouse button on the map or on the minimap.<br>
        </p>
    
